00:30:55.564 --> 00:30:56.735
Mom.

509
00:31:00.505 --> 00:31:02.405
Why are you like this?

510
00:31:04.114 --> 00:31:07.485
When we went to Yong Hyun's wedding,

511
00:31:07.485 --> 00:31:10.284
you told me the wedding was just a noisy and money-spending event.

512
00:31:10.655 --> 00:31:13.455
We had a family meeting and introduced each other.

513
00:31:13.554 --> 00:31:15.054
Why do we have to have a wedding?

514
00:31:17.354 --> 00:31:20.394
I feel like they are looking down on us.

515
00:31:21.394 --> 00:31:23.935
Do you think it's a good thing they think you are innocent and kind?

516
00:31:24.034 --> 00:31:27.064
That means they want you to listen to them all the time...

517
00:31:27.064 --> 00:31:29.435
and have no opinion. Did you know that?

518
00:31:29.765 --> 00:31:31.205
It feels like they are looking down on you...

519
00:31:31.205 --> 00:31:34.275
because you are living with him before getting married.

520
00:31:36.275 --> 00:31:38.314
Why are you so twisted?

521
00:31:38.314 --> 00:31:40.314
It's true that they are looking down on you.

522
00:31:40.314 --> 00:31:42.284
Let me ask you more.

523
00:31:43.915 --> 00:31:45.015
Why do you...

524
00:31:46.255 --> 00:31:47.955
want to get married?

525
00:31:49.025 --> 00:31:51.925
What do you mean?

526
00:31:52.094 --> 00:31:55.725
Is it weird to get married even though I'm 30?

527
00:31:55.725 --> 00:31:56.834
What about your work?

528
00:31:57.864 --> 00:31:58.995
Are you not going to write?

529
00:32:03.604 --> 00:32:04.804
I'm not going to write anymore.

530
00:32:07.005 --> 00:32:08.104
I quit.

531
00:32:08.104 --> 00:32:09.874
You chose the marriage as your job.

532
00:32:10.445 --> 00:32:11.515
You are not actually getting married then.

533
00:32:11.515 --> 00:32:13.344
Why? There's nothing wrong with that.

534
00:32:13.344 --> 00:32:16.685
Do you think I paid for your college tuition for this?

535
00:32:17.185 --> 00:32:20.354
Is this what your dad gets after paying for you that much?

536
00:32:21.284 --> 00:32:22.554
How can you just become like this?

537
00:32:23.455 --> 00:32:24.725
What can I do?

538
00:32:25.225 --> 00:32:27.025
