00:52:16.895 --> 00:52:17.964
Thank you for coming.

872
00:52:18.234 --> 00:52:20.105
- Hello. - Welcome.

873
00:52:22.265 --> 00:52:23.404
Hello.

874
00:52:24.205 --> 00:52:25.404
- Congratulations. - Congratulations.

