876
00:52:28.504 --> 00:52:29.645
Hello.

877
00:52:29.714 --> 00:52:31.274
Go on in.

878
00:52:34.515 --> 00:52:35.645
Where are you going?

879
00:52:36.084 --> 00:52:37.185
To the restroom.

880
00:52:50.895 --> 00:52:52.464
The bride went to the restroom.

881
00:52:53.665 --> 00:52:54.765
Is that so?

882
00:53:13.125 --> 00:53:16.185
Do you have anything to say?

883
00:53:17.855 --> 00:53:20.725
No, I don't.

884
00:53:22.194 --> 00:53:23.794
Then why are you coming out from there?

885
00:53:26.364 --> 00:53:28.864
I thought it was a bathroom.

886
00:53:32.075 --> 00:53:33.174
Mom.

887
00:53:35.345 --> 00:53:38.745
Why did you ask for his number?

888
00:53:40.884 --> 00:53:42.515
Why?

889
00:53:43.084 --> 00:53:45.915
Can I not ask my son-in-law's number?

890
00:53:48.125 --> 00:53:49.754
I wonder what you are going to say to him.

891
00:53:50.524 --> 00:53:51.694
What?

892
00:53:52.625 --> 00:53:55.794
I'm even doing the wedding as you wanted.

893
00:53:56.435 --> 00:53:58.834
So you can stop talking about stupid things to him.

894
00:53:59.705 --> 00:54:01.634
If you do that to him again,

895
00:54:02.265 --> 00:54:05.035
I will be really upset.

896
00:54:09.475 --> 00:54:10.544
Did you hear me?

897
00:54:11.975 --> 00:54:13.044
I wish...

898
00:54:15.185 --> 00:54:17.884
you could have a daughter like you.

899
00:54:33.404 --> 00:54:35.504
- The ceremony will start soon. - I see.

900
00:54:37.234 --> 00:54:40.745
By the way, Is that black bag Se Hee's?

901
00:54:41.205 --> 00:54:43.044
Yes, why?

902
00:54:43.444 --> 00:54:46.015
Your mom asked me about it. She wanted to give something to him.

903
00:54:46.015 --> 00:54:47.614
Did my mom say so?

904
00:54:47.685 --> 00:54:49.685
Yes, she put something in that bag.

905
00:54:53.924 --> 00:54:55.254
I knew she was going to do that.

906
00:54:56.725 --> 00:54:57.794
What is it?

907
00:55:04.294 --> 00:55:06.765
Nam Se Hee and Yoon Ji Ho's wedding ceremony...

908
00:55:06.864 --> 00:55:10.075
will start soon.

909
00:55:10.504 --> 00:55:13.845
Please be seated.

910
00:55:32.855 --> 00:55:33.964
Se Hee.

911
00:55:36.712 --> 00:55:37.841
What?

912
00:55:40.755 --> 00:55:41.864
Se Hee.

913
00:55:44.612 --> 00:55:46.041
What? Why?

914
00:55:46.143 --> 00:55:47.342
How should I know?

915
00:55:51.212 --> 00:55:52.283
Excuse me.

916
00:55:53.422 --> 00:55:54.482
Ji Ho.

917
00:56:13.373 --> 00:56:16.413
I'm Ji Ho's mom.

918
00:56:17.243 --> 00:56:20.413
