921
00:56:28.522 --> 00:56:31.053
She's my first daughter, you know.

922
00:56:32.022 --> 00:56:33.922
She's like my husband sometimes,

923
00:56:34.362 --> 00:56:37.692
and she's also like my friend.

924
00:56:45.433 --> 00:56:47.272
She's scared of her dad,

925
00:56:47.803 --> 00:56:49.612
and she had to give up a lot because of her younger brother.

926
00:56:52.712 --> 00:56:54.583
Because she met someone like me as her mother,

927
00:56:55.413 --> 00:56:57.783
she has gone through a lot.

928
00:57:02.583 --> 00:57:06.192
Thankfully, not like me, she's really smart.

929
00:57:06.192 --> 00:57:08.962
(Certificate of Award)

930
00:57:09.263 --> 00:57:11.192
I was relieved because I thought...

931
00:57:11.763 --> 00:57:13.562
she was not going to live like me.

932
00:57:25.172 --> 00:57:26.683
I guess,

933
00:57:26.913 --> 00:57:29.612
being smart is nothing...

934
00:57:31.382 --> 00:57:34.623
if you don't have a rich family these days.

935
00:57:41.263 --> 00:57:43.993
Se Hee,

936
00:57:45.062 --> 00:57:48.962
