957
00:59:03.272 --> 00:59:05.542
Se Hee, I'll be with her.

958
00:59:05.573 --> 00:59:07.783
You should go first now. They are waiting for you.

959
00:59:14.252 --> 00:59:15.323
Where's the tissue?

960
00:59:16.393 --> 00:59:17.922
What should I do with her makeup?

961
00:59:19.763 --> 00:59:22.223
Stop crying, Ji Ho.

962
00:59:50.893 --> 00:59:52.022
Is it hard to...

963
00:59:53.292 --> 00:59:54.792
stop crying?

964
01:00:03.272 --> 01:00:04.333
If that's the case,

965
01:00:05.433 --> 01:00:06.743
we should go together.

966
01:00:11.272 --> 01:00:12.942
